  "about": "Souya Kawata, known as \"Angry,\" is the Fourth Division Vice-Captain of the Tokyo Manji Gang. He is the younger twin brother of Nahoya Kawata (Smiley).\n\nAngry is of short stature and small build. He has voluminous curly, bright turquoise hair that matches the hues of his eyes and two silver earrings on his right earlobe. His face is constantly set in a snarl, making the veins on his face prominent, hence his famous nickname \"Angry.\" He wears the traditional Tokyo Manji Gang uniform when embarking on missions but always matches outfits with his twin brother when out on personal endeavors.\n\nContrary to his appearance, Angry is kind and pacifist. He cares a lot about his friends and wishes to protect them at all costs. Smiley states that Angry is too nice to beat anyone up.\n\n\n(Source: Tokyo Revengers Wiki, edited)",
  "note": null,
  "source": "anime"
